column5: ALEX....Bly and I hope you are having a great birthday!  I'll let you tell everyone how old you are......haha.  Have an awesome day bro-in-law!!
Happy Birthday Alex, have a great day.  Joey
Have a great day Alex, I hope you've been able to get out fishing...  Maureen
All the best on your day!  Easton
Happy Birthday Alex, now GET OUT THERE AND FIND A FISH FOR THE TOURNEY!!!  Have a great one!  HearingFish
thank you everyone and as  a matter of fact I have Friday off so I'll be going out then.
Happy to ya Bud,when ya coming down this way for some cats and stripers? Joe
Happy birthday to you Alex. Hope you had a good one and many more.
